<h1 id="installation">Installation</h1>
<hr />

<ul>
  <li>Fork the repository. &lt;iframe src="https://ghbtns.com/github-btn.html?user=songkong&amp;repo=Blog&amp;type=fork&amp;count=true" frameborder="0" scrolling="0" width="170px" height="20px"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;</li>
  <li>Edit <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">_config.yml</code> file.</li>
  <li>Add your own <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">projects</code> in <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">_includes/projects.html</code>.</li>
  <li>Change <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">domain name</code> in <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">CNAME</code>.</li>
  <li>Replace <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">favicon.ico</code> with your website icon.</li>
  <li>Change <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">avatar.jpg</code> and <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">cartoon-avatar.jpg</code> in <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">assets/images</code>.</li>
  <li>Edit <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">LICENSE.md</code> and <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">README.md</code>.</li>
</ul>

<blockquote>
  <p>I use two categories for posts in my blog, <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Tech</code> and <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Life</code>. If you want to add other categories, remember to modify <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">_includes/post-list-pagination</code>, <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">_layouts/post-list.html</code> and <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">assets/js/script.js</code> to add <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Tabs</code> and <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Paginations</code> for every category posts.</p>
</blockquote>

